org.apache.hadoop.metrics2.impl

Class SinkQueue<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.metrics2.impl.SinkQueue<T>

  •  class SinkQueue<T>
extends Object
    A half-blocking (nonblocking for producers, blocking for consumers) queue for metrics sinks. New elements are dropped when the queue is full to preserve "interesting" elements at the onset of queue filling events
